{"tid":83153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真討論］咩叫控制節奏","createTime":"2017-01-16T13:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T04:59:18.000Z","uid":4706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f346f33f6b591e36a884ad30473ca088be63cdb","tid":83153,"uid":4706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"成日聽到控制節奏好似有d虛<br />\n好似知又好似唔知咁<br />\n到底有無一個清晰準確既定義？<br />\n睇精華係咪唔會睇得出？<br />\n<br />\n進攻勁/打進攻足球既隊通常會公認控制節奏好出色既球員，例如拼圖王，派路呢d<br />\n咁防守出色，打穩守突擊既隊重唔重視控制節奏？有無球隊同球員例子？<br />\n<br />\n定係佢地最大目的就係打亂對方陣腳，所以唔太講求呢一部分？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1ae860425696cc3281d9ef2cf4dfc9874fea71","tid":83153,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"節奏一亂 呼吸就亂<br />\n呼吸一亂 波紋就散"},{"pid":"ddb6156946614b383372cebdae56aa6dc157d5ce","tid":83153,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:49:28.000Z","msg":"一隊波冇可能可以90分鐘打快波，通常都要時快時慢，咁咪要一個識控制節奏既人，好似魔迪，小白咁。有時要調節返成場波個節奏，比班人休息下有好，變打法都好"},{"pid":"4c1d3ee3f3de76c3591a87159e578adb003c6efe","tid":83153,"uid":33103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"應快則快，應慢則慢<br />\n在後場猜猜下，會突然放直線ko 對手"},{"pid":"a931bdd2c6eea1caccccf22676adddeebba2c181","tid":83153,"uid":38543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"1212隻腳"},{"pid":"72920679cab9f4ea11066809e56f45320822588d","tid":83153,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"打反擊識快<br />\n打穩守識慢 = 控制節奏<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎睇到打防反 條友原地插花<br />\n等對面隊埋位先開始攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04386c04d2411bb7ebf383dd01e14c510c972402","tid":83153,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"損有餘而補不足"},{"pid":"033c52691ae6b66271a499ae9717aa5e3f130b8a","tid":83153,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"應去則去 收放自如<br />\n好似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffab1076c1ddd7596598253b22257896cc7abd5","tid":83153,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"時代節奏<br />\n童夢 主題曲<br />\n<br />\n曲:唐奕聰 詞:因葵 唱:劉錫明 <br />\n<br />\n節奏緊湊 就是沒法會停留<br />\n緊迫的節奏 似要你我爭鬥<br />\n節奏緊湊 並未讓我再回頭<br />\n緊張的節奏 看似世界所有<br />\n怎追究 AH...<br />\n<br />\n不可以偷 不可以收<br />\n時日那會停在等候 <br />\n難盡量佔有 豈有萬代千秋<br />\n來讓我寄情極荒謬<br />\n如果可擁有 光陰會有出售<br />\n無用再愁困無雖遺漏<br />\n現在縱有只夠 只夠日夕擔憂<br />\n然後自覺惆悵中再走<br />\n<br />\n世界緊湊 路上沒法會停留<br />\n緊迫的節奏 刺痛你我傷口<br />\n世界緊湊 莫問道理去尋求<br />\n緊張的節奏 看似世界所有<br />\n怎追究 AH...<br />\n<br />\n到最後 到最後<br />\n仍不可永久!"},{"pid":"05bde04ac185b05ef8fb20aeaf02cdef8bc294c2","tid":83153,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打反擊識快<br />\n打穩守識慢 = 控制節奏<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎睇到打防反 條友原地插花<br />\n等對面隊埋位先開始攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n防反係唔等對面對面隊埋位打快攻wor..."},{"pid":"f8679fc916bbd2c8e81f69667ddb6cc5e75716fd","tid":83153,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打反擊識快<br />\n打穩守識慢 = 控制節奏<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎睇到打防反 條友原地插花<br />\n等對面隊埋位先開始攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又串呀朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4379001dd6829afe8ca023bd105f3a1dc06765d3","tid":83153,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"利記個陣沙比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3098d4d1fa08c3ed37675428b8bf69df199b23d","tid":83153,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"沙維係呢樣野簡直就係教材級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a3ded59b5b8a4e0a2789deedc887d9946fd87f","tid":83153,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打反擊識快<br />\n打穩守識慢 = 控制節奏<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎睇到打防反 條友原地插花<br />\n等對面隊埋位先開始攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n防反係唔等對面對面隊埋位打快攻wor...</blockquote><br />\nUp乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼唔知打防反 正常係唔等對面隊埋位 就即刻去攻咩<br />\n但大把垃圾中場/前鋒 係要插下花等下人先進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84ceed3d7346e7aa6dbdf74eb1296a45255661f","tid":83153,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙維係呢樣野簡直就係教材級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa6a254df8851cc83110f017bab3e170d3c94a9","tid":83153,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1212隻腳</blockquote><br />\n果個係咪你老襟嚟㗎"},{"pid":"6d53294f1a318c05fb0329def2d468abacc2e54a","tid":83153,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>節奏一亂 呼吸就亂<br />\n呼吸一亂 波紋就散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太陽波紋！！！"},{"pid":"45960289c55d407d8f43a98c0d1709327f1420c8","tid":83153,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打反擊識快<br />\n打穩守識慢 = 控制節奏<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎睇到打防反 條友原地插花<br />\n等對面隊埋位先開始攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n防反係唔等對面對面隊埋位打快攻wor...</blockquote><br />\nUp乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼唔知打防反 正常係唔等對面隊埋位 就即刻去攻咩<br />\n但大把垃圾中場/前鋒 係要插下花等下人先進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近兩年既朗肥係好例子<br />\n<br />\n有長傳能力  於是一打反擊隊友就想交波比佢分<br />\n<br />\n條肥西盲控定  自轉   永遠無話一腳分波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f181150ca642ada6bcf739fcfda167cfc3ca7591","tid":83153,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"打快攻唔會拖波<br />\n打組織唔會亂俾直線<br />\n領先緊識得控場"},{"pid":"187bd50e55bf548fa238ef2b657fe750e5549603","tid":83153,"uid":46086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"同陰力同出一徹<br />\n明白陰力就可以了解控制節奏"},{"pid":"2e446956c3002bf0a3ae14404e14ee96ffca2192","tid":83153,"uid":53808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"反而想知英文點講<br />\n想睇吓外國分析"},{"pid":"f230996ac56d39b747ec6fc53c30eed310fe520b","tid":83153,"uid":43696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而想知英文點講<br />\n想睇吓外國分析</blockquote><br />\ndictate tempo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係控制節奏"},{"pid":"1e27de627d70f91fefcf1a0717fe07e494eda1f7","tid":83153,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e5d1220a4059c982d43d6a4cc2b3ca553180ee","tid":83153,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"控球後衛"}]}